Hello, thank you for calling Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Lawrence Rogers. May I have your name, please?

Hi Lawrence, my name is Amanda Bell.

Thank you, Amanda. How can I assist you today?

I'm calling because I'm unhappy about a refund I requested and haven’t received yet.

I’m sorry to hear that, Amanda. Let me help you resolve this. Could you please provide your order number?

Sure, it's two zero one zero three.

Thank you. One more thing, may I have the date of purchase?

Yes, it was on September tenth.

Got it, Amanda. I’ll look into this immediately. Thank you for providing the details.

I appreciate your patience and apologize for any inconvenience. Thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. Have a great day!
